1
00:00:05,300 --> 00:00:07,020
(Our first meeting)

2
00:00:07,030 --> 00:00:09,430
Welcome to the Balance Island.

3
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:11,070
What is this road called?

4
00:00:11,070 --> 00:00:12,840
Love Road.

5
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,880
Neat and sunny.

6
00:00:15,190 --> 00:00:17,550
No, I'm just kinda reserved.

7
00:00:17,550 --> 00:00:18,660
So any type is fine,

8
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:19,760
as long as she is beautiful.

9
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,710
Then why didn't you

10
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,390
talk much?

11
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:22,370
I might talk more

12
00:00:22,370 --> 00:00:23,440
once we become acquainted.

13
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:25,360
My answer is Zhan Jiaming.

14
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,040
Why are you all

15
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,550
