16
00:00:28,070 --> 00:00:30,680
Who seems a bit hard to pursue?

17
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:32,270
She feels a bit uncomfortable.

18
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:35,260
=Live and Love S2=

19
00:00:35,260 --> 00:00:38,580
=We're on Balance Island=

20
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,860
(Balance Island)

21
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:52,630
Hello.

22
00:00:53,590 --> 00:00:54,470
Can you cook?

23
00:00:54,790 --> 00:00:56,680
Well, I'd say I can cook.

24
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:57,910
But I'm not that good at it.

25
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,150
Just home-cooked meal.

26
00:00:59,150 --> 00:01:00,080
Home cooking is okay.

27
00:01:00,470 --> 00:01:01,470
You're too modest.

28
00:01:01,590 --> 00:01:02,240
No.

29
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,520
Instant noodles.

30
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,310
Yes, instant noodle.

31
00:01:04,310 --> 00:01:05,360
River snail rice noodles.

32
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:06,120
Oh?

33
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:06,800
You like it?

34
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,830
I like the non-spicy one.

35
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,310
What? Non-spicy?

36
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:11,510
I can only handle a little bit

37
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,760
