38
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,040
So we are both "fast" food lovers.

39
00:01:15,510 --> 00:01:16,870
What does "fast" food lover mean?

40
00:01:17,190 --> 00:01:18,760
A gourmet who only eats "fast" food.

41
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,040
Have a seat.

42
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,230
I'll sit here.

43
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,800
I'll sit across from you.

44
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:27,400
Then I'll sit here.

45
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,000
Sure.

46
00:01:28,590 --> 00:01:30,120
They are busy boiling water.

47
00:01:31,910 --> 00:01:34,310
Welcome to the Balance Island.

48
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:42,830
Before entering the island,

49
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:46,120
you will engage in a competition.

50
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:49,260
(What's going on??)

51
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,040
I think

52
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:58,080
it should be boys.

53
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:01,480
Let me check.

54
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,120
Let me check.

55
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,870
Thanks, but no.

56
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:16,860
(Winners head to the Balance Island.)

57
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,550
Is someone coming?

58
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,600
Maybe.

59
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,390
What is this road called?

60
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:41,000
Love Road.

61
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:43,830
The competition is over.

62
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:46,720
Everyone, please get on the bus and leave.

63
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:51,540
(Losers head to the Penal Colony.)

64
00:02:51,550 --> 00:02:52,520
It happened so fast.

65
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,550
Unbelievable.

66
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:55,550
(Still processing)

67
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:57,110
