68
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:59,240
No impression.

69
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,000
(Not at all)
They're smart.

70
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:03,880
Right from the beginning,

71
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,780
