85
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,550
That's the way to go.

86
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,750
We were going to compete.

87
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,160
Why were they just standing there?

88
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,830
They just took a look and won the game?

89
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:37,260
(Balance Island)

90
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,390
