94
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:47,550
Then go ahead.

95
00:03:47,550 --> 00:03:48,600
She must be an extrovert.

96
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,060
(Disagrees)
Obviously...

97
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,110
