98
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,800
INFP (Mediator).

99
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,550
Didn't she say she's extrovert?

100
00:03:59,390 --> 00:04:01,880
But I'm half introverted
and half extroverted.

101
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,160
Right now it's

102
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:04,830
ENTP (Debater).

103
