We're the same.

104
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,670
You too?

105
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:09,080
And me.

106
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,000
Both of you are

107
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,800
ENTP (Debater).

108
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,270
Yeah.

109
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,880
Then all of you are purple.

110
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,630
The Purple Man.

111
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,510
What are you?

112
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,510
I am green.

113
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,320
You are introverted.

114
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:18,950
Yes.

115
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,600
Trust your intuition.

116
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,320
INTJ (Architect).

117
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,160
You got three right.

118
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,830
INFJ (Advocate).

119
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:27,320
Right.

120
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,480
Guess what mine is?

121
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,320
You are introverted.

122
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,760
Me?

123
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,670
Then why didn't you

124
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:36,600
