127
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:44,480
Okay.

128
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,550
ENFJ (Protagonist).

129
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:49,740
(Did I guess right?)

130
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:51,920
Yes.

131
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,200
Spot on.

132
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:55,380
