136
00:05:01,350 --> 00:05:02,790
She's really hard to...

137
00:05:02,790 --> 00:05:03,510
You wouldn't be...

138
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:04,600
ENTJ (Commander), right?

139
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:09,790
No.

140
00:05:11,350 --> 00:05:12,760
