142
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:16,230
ENFP (Campaigner).

143
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:16,950
Ah, puppy.

144
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,830
Happy puppy.

145
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:23,200
Actually, I don't really believe
in this thing.

146
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:25,040
In terms of MBTI,

147
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,640
