181
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,480
Yes, this is ours.

182
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,270
Goodbye.

183
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,160
Bye.

184
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:35,510
