221
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:31,600
So the three of us...

222
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,720
It's fine. We can...

223
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:33,950
Alright.

224
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:34,760
