227
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,640
Yes.

228
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,230
Okay.

229
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:39,540
We'll help you move your luggage.

230
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:40,550
You can go back

231
00:07:40,550 --> 00:07:41,550
