Mind your step.

236
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:54,950
Thank you.

237
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:55,600
No problem.

238
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,110
Thanks for your hard work.

239
00:07:57,110 --> 00:07:58,320
(Arena; Dorm; Square;
Dinning room; Balance Zone)

240
00:07:58,330 --> 00:07:58,760
