299
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,640
The premise is that

300
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,400
she needs to look good.

301
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,200
But it still depends on the feeling.

302
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,640
Men who think that way

303
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,910
have the highest standard.

304
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:52,590
Mmm.

305
00:09:52,590 --> 00:09:53,320
Because he can

306
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,710
