307
00:09:54,710 --> 00:09:55,350
to a girl.

308
00:09:56,590 --> 00:09:57,200
Well...

309
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,840
What about you?

310
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,590
What about you two?

311
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,550
The type that she and I like

312
00:10:04,550 --> 00:10:05,080
is different.

313
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:06,650
Tell me about it.

314
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,200
Take a guess.

315
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,910
Then mature.

316
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,200
Nah.

317
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,520
Then a "puppy-like" guy.

318
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:14,320
Yes, I like...

319
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,590
But that is a bit...

320
00:10:17,470 --> 00:10:19,150
too general.

321
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,350
Sunny little "puppy".

322
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,910
I like...

323
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:24,230
a bit quieter type,

324
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:27,200
who's able to enjoy his own world

325
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,520
and can also share with me

326
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,710
his own world.

327
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:31,670
You elevate the conversation.

328
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:34,000
Now we're talk about

329
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,710
spiritual world.

330
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:36,400
Yes, it's a deeper level.

331
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,000
Then let's talk about

332
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,960
the appearance.

333
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,910
I don't like muscle men.

334
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,230
She prefers less muscle.

335
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,000
Delicate.

336
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
A bit delicate.

337
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:44,840
Delicate and quiet.

338
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,520
I hope you can meet your delicate boy.

339
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,710
Your delicate boy.

340
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,520
Then you two should be just the opposite.

341
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:54,960
Right, what about you?

342
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,400
We like the same type.

343
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,640
I like someone neat and sunny.

344
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:02,710
I don't feel like I'd like someone sloppy.

345
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,590
I have something for you.

346
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:06,440
What is this?

347
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,760
The things I brought for everyone.

348
00:11:07,900 --> 00:11:08,840
You even brought gifts.

349
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,520
Yes.

350
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:13,440
Put them there.

351
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,790
Wait until they arrive.

352
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:19,320
Come on, I've got something for you.

353
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,470
Specialties from my hometown.

354
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,440
Thank you.

355
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,640
It includes black goji berry

356
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:27,030
and also cordyceps.

357
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:27,760
Here.

358
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,640
Thank you.

359
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:30,440
So thoughtful.

360
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:32,200
Thanks.

361
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,200
Very delicious.

362
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:43,900
(Yum yum)

363
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:45,370
You can have cordyceps

364
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,230
to reduce fatigue.

365
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,000
Eating this might cause a nosebleed, right?

366
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,840
It really can't be them

367
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,840
cooking for us, can it?

368
00:11:55,230 --> 00:11:56,960
I think it's them.

369
00:11:57,300 --> 00:11:58,840
(Very likely)
Because of the time.

370
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:01,880
It feels like a normal chef
would've finished already.

371
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,380
(A long wait)

372
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,540
(Welcome to Overcooked)

373
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:07,910
Why can't I find it?

374
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:09,910
I want is shrimp paste.

375
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:10,840
Do you have some?

376
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,590
Where is chicken?

377
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:12,280
Did you see it?

378
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,710
(Missing ingredient)
No spare ribs.

379
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:15,000
(Unrecognizable)
Meat?

380
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,000
No cucumber either.

381
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,550
Did you see any onions?

382
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:18,910
Only two boards?

383
00:12:18,910 --> 00:12:20,350
(Missing tool)
We need more cutting boards.

384
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,910
(In a flurry)
Oh my god.

385
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:24,400
They are on the Balance Island.

386
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:25,790
We are on some kind of Hell Island.

387
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,880
It's really exhausting.

388
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:29,790
Now we know

389
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:31,400
the importance of those two keys.

390
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:32,880
Right.

391
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,660
(Regretting)

392
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,760
I really regret it.

393
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,500
(Let it be. Whatever.)

394
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,470
I'm really curious

395
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:41,470
what they're doing.

396
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,960
We are working hard cooking.

397
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:46,760
Do you enjoy the process of cooking?

398
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,030
Honestly,

399
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:49,790
not really.

400
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,150
"Honestly".

401
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:53,960
I wouldn't spend two or three hours

402
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:56,110
making a meal for myself alone.

403
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:57,550
I think it's quite a waste of time.

404
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:00,710
So, do guys who can cook

405
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:02,400
get extra points in your eyes?

406
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:02,880
Yes.

407
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,110
Definitely.

408
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:05,840
It is a plus.

409
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,230
Yeah, it is.

410
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:08,960
That's bad.

411
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,760
If you can't cook, order food.

412
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,670
Exactly.

413
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,780
(Not a big problem)

414
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,590
I have beef jerky, do you want some?

415
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:16,880
Beef jerky?

416
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:17,470
Sure.

417
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:18,030
I have too.

418
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,910
Right, you're from Qinghai Province.

419
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:20,880
I want to have some.

420
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,550
I'll go get it.

421
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:27,910
Among the girls here,

422
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,670
which one do you feel
the most chemistry with?

423
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:33,080
I'm still looking around.

424
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,760
At the moment.

425
00:13:33,760 --> 00:13:34,150
And you?

426
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:34,860
First impression.

427
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,960
Well, the time we spent together...

428
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,350
To be honest,

429
00:13:38,350 --> 00:13:39,470
you and that one...

430
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:41,320
The one in white clothes.

431
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:43,110
Right?

432
00:13:43,110 --> 00:13:44,350
I feel like you're towards...

433
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:46,350
But I'm not artistic.

434
00:13:46,350 --> 00:13:47,470
She likes artistic type.

435
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:49,000
Let me tell you.

436
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,710
Right when we first arrived,

437
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:52,080
she stood up in the front.

438
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:52,760
You could tell

439
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,760
she's the lively type of person.

440
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:55,280
Yes.

441
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,590
Then I suddenly felt like

442
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:57,390
you two...

443
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,800
seem to have a bit of chemistry.

444
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,280
You know?

445
00:13:59,280 --> 00:13:59,760
Really?

446
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:00,200
Yes.

447
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:00,960
Here.

448
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,790
Let's just use mine.

449
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:06,080
Thank you.

450
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,670
No problem.

451
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,320
Thank you.

452
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:09,910
I brought this.

453
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:12,380
