454
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:14,540
This is...

455
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:15,230
Repellent patch.

456
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:15,960
Here you go.

457
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,590
Yes.

458
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:17,880
So cute.

459
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,150
It is a princess.

460
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,030
"Frozen".

461
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:22,760
Thank you.

462
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,150
I can use it right now.

463
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:24,840
Thank you.

464
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,230
I'm good.

465
00:14:26,230 --> 00:14:27,280
Come on.

466
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:27,880
Thank you.

467
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:32,550
That's great.

468
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:34,640
I have thirteen cats

469
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,400
