471
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:40,200
My home is like a zoo.

472
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,470
Do you like cats or dogs?

473
00:14:42,690 --> 00:14:44,080
I'm actually allergic to cats (fur).

474
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,280
So I'm not living at home.

475
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:46,590
I prefer dogs.

476
00:14:46,590 --> 00:14:47,710
My family has a dog.

477
00:14:47,910 --> 00:14:49,080
I have two.

478
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:50,110
You have two?

479
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,110
Mine is a Bichon.

480
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,470
Mine are mixed-breed.

481
00:14:52,470 --> 00:14:53,840
I adopted them.

482
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,200
What's the breed?

483
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:55,840
Poodle?

484
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,150
Bichon.

485
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:58,710
I don't like cats.

486
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,200
I also don't like cats.

487
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,350
Then do you like dogs

488
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:04,230
